			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="C001083">Mr. Carney</sponsor> (for
			 himself and <cosponsor name-id="F000451">Mr. Fitzpatrick</cosponsor>)
			 introduced the following bill; which was referred to the
			 <committee-name committee-id="HIF00">Committee on Energy and
			 Commerce</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
